{"id":956,"parent_id":949,"book_id":1,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":956,"title":"Zechariah 7","subtitle":"","short_title":"Zech.","uri":"/scriptures/ot/zech/7","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 7"],[".studySummary",["i","The Lord reproves hypocrisy in fasts—He calls upon the people to show mercy and compassion and to live godly lives."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/ot/zech/7.1","order":"02.39.007.62929"},["b","1"],"And it came to pass in the fourth year of king Darius,",["i","that"],"the word of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"came unto Zechariah in the fourth",["i","day"],"of the ninth month,",["i","even"],"in Chisleu;"],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/ot/zech/7.2","order":"02.39.007.62930"},["b","2"],"When they had sent unto the house of God Sherezer and Regem-melech, and their men, to pray before the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],","],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/ot/zech/7.3","order":"02.39.007.62931"},["b","3"],["i","And"],"to speak unto the priests which",["i","were"],"in the house of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"of hosts, and to the prophets, saying, Should I weep in the fifth month, separating myself, as I have done these so many years?"],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/ot/zech/7.4","order":"02.39.007.62932"},["b","4"],"¶Then came the word of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"of hosts unto me, saying,"],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/ot/zech/7.5","order":"02.39.007.62933"},["b","5"],"Speak unto all the people of the land, and to the priests, saying, When ye fasted and mourned in the fifth and seventh",["i","month,"],"even those seventy years, did ye at all",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_5a"},"fast"],"unto me,",["i","even"],"to me?"],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/ot/zech/7.6","order":"02.39.007.62934"},["b","6"],"And when ye did eat, and when ye did drink, did not ye eat",["i","for yourselves,"],"and drink",["i","for yourselves?"]],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/ot/zech/7.7","order":"02.39.007.62935"},["b","7"],["i","Should ye"],"not",["i","hear"],"the words which the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"hath cried by the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_7a"},"former"],"prophets, when Jerusalem was inhabited and in prosperity, and the cities thereof round about her, when",["i","men"],"inhabited the south and the plain?"],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/ot/zech/7.8","order":"02.39.007.62936"},["b","8"],"¶And the word of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"came unto Zechariah, saying,"],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/ot/zech/7.9","order":"02.39.007.62937"},["b","9"],"Thus speaketh the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"of hosts, saying, Execute true",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_9a"},"judgment"],", and shew",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_9b"},"mercy"],"and",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_9c"},"compassions"],"every man to his brother:"],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/ot/zech/7.10","order":"02.39.007.62938"},["b","10"],"And",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_10a"},"oppress"],"not the widow, nor the fatherless, the stranger, nor the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_10b"},"poor"],"; and let none of you imagine evil against his brother in your heart."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/ot/zech/7.11","order":"02.39.007.62939"},["b","11"],"But they refused to hearken, and pulled away the shoulder, and stopped their ears, that they should not hear."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/ot/zech/7.12","order":"02.39.007.62940"},["b","12"],"Yea, they made their hearts",["i","as"],"an adamant",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_12a"},"stone"],", lest they should hear the law, and the words which the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"of hosts hath sent in his spirit by the former",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_12b"},"prophets"],": therefore came a great wrath from the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"of hosts."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/ot/zech/7.13","order":"02.39.007.62941"},["b","13"],"Therefore it is come to pass,",["i","that"],"as he cried, and they would not hear; so",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_13a"},"they"],["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_13b"},"cried"],", and I would not hear, saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"of hosts:"],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/ot/zech/7.14","order":"02.39.007.62942"},["b","14"],"But I",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_14a"},"scattered"],"them with a whirlwind among all the nations whom they knew not. Thus the land was desolate after them, that no man passed through nor returned: for they laid the pleasant land desolate."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"5a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/zech/7.5a","order":"02.39.007.62943"},["b","5a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/matt/6.16"},"Matt. 6:16"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/13.16.16-18"},"3 Ne. 13:16 (16–18)"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/fast-fasting"},"TG Fast, Fasting"],"."],["div",{"id":"7a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/zech/7.7a","order":"02.39.007.62945"},["b","7a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/84.57.14,54-57"},"D&C 84:57 (14, 54–57)"],"."],["div",{"id":"9a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/zech/7.9a","order":"02.39.007.62947"},["b","9a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/justice"},"TG Justice"],"."],["div",{"id":"9b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/zech/7.9b","order":"02.39.007.62949"},["b","9b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/mercy"},"TG Mercy"],"."],["div",{"id":"9c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/zech/7.9c","order":"02.39.007.62951"},["b","9c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/charity"},"TG Charity"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/compassion"},"Compassion"],"."],["div",{"id":"10a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/zech/7.10a","order":"02.39.007.62953"},["b","10a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/22.7.7-14"},"Ezek. 22:7 (7–14)"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/cruelty"},"TG Cruelty"],"."],["div",{"id":"10b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/zech/7.10b","order":"02.39.007.62955"},["b","10b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/prov/22.22"},"Prov. 22:22"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/4.26.16-26"},"Mosiah 4:26 (16–26)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/hel/4.12"},"Hel. 4:12"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/42.30.30-39,71"},"D&C 42:30 (30–39, 71)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/83.6"},"83:6"],"."],["div",{"id":"12a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/zech/7.12a","order":"02.39.007.62957"},["b","12a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/matt/13.20"},"Matt. 13:20"],"."],["div",{"id":"12b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/zech/7.12b","order":"02.39.007.62959"},["b","12b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/matt/11.13"},"Matt. 11:13"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/3.20"},"1 Ne. 3:20"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/15.13"},"Mosiah 15:13"],"."],["div",{"id":"13a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/zech/7.13a","order":"02.39.007.62961"},["b","13a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/lam/1.2.1-3"},"Lam. 1:2 (1–3)"],"."],["div",{"id":"13b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/zech/7.13b","order":"02.39.007.62963"},["b","13b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/god-access-to"},"TG God, Access to"],"."],["div",{"id":"14a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/zech/7.14a","order":"02.39.007.62965"},["b","14a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/israel-ten-lost-tribes-of"},"TG Israel, Ten Lost Tribes of"],"."]]}
